Package: apidirect
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: API Direct CLI - Rapid API deployment tool
 API Direct CLI is a command-line tool that transforms your code into
 deployed APIs in minutes. It features:
 .
  * Auto-detection of API frameworks and languages
  * Container-based deployment with auto-generated Dockerfiles
  * Built-in API marketplace with monetization
  * Environment variable management
  * Real-time log streaming and monitoring
  * Multi-language support (Python, Node.js, Go, Ruby)
 .
 This package provides the apidirect command-line tool.